                     <interp inst="t18170917-47-person347" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner into custody, and found two half-crowns and two shillings, upon him.</p>
               <p>MR. BOYD. It is the money I marked.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. It is usual for the porter to put out the gass, which I went to do.</p>
               <p>
